Company Profile:Global Lingo
provides professional transcription, minute-taking, translation and
interpreting services. We're one of the fastest growing language agencies in
the UK, and one of the only agencies to specialise in minute taking and
transcription, as well as translation and interpreting services of the highest
quality.With offices in London, Leeds, Singapore and Cluj in Romania, we are growing
really quickly, helping to ensure that we are always flexible enough to
accommodate our clients’ requirements. We focus on providing our clients with
accurate language services, which deliver value-for-money to their
organisations.Our clients include three serving prime ministers, two of the world's leading
oil companies, three of the world's largest banks and one of the top three
Premiership football clubs.
Job Description:If you are looking
for a Strategic Account Manager role in a company expanding massively and
you want to help shape its future direction. We’re looking for special people
with drive and passion. We’re known for delivering only the highest quality
translation, interpreting and transcription services and a huge part of this is
down to our dedication to customer care and service. If you can help us make a
difference then we want to hear from you.
Based in our Singapore office, your primary responsibility will be the strategic
account management of some of our existing translation, transcription and
interpreting client base. Your role will be to work with these contacts and
find new ones within the organisations to expand Global Lingo’s reach.
You don’t need any
experience of working in the language industry because we’ll supply you with
all the support and training you need.
We are an Equal
Opportunities employer and welcome applications from all eligible candidates but not agencies.Key ResponsibilitiesDevelop existing
